==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Septenary
<hw>Sep"ten*a*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>septenairus</ets>, from <ets>septeni</ets> seven each,
<ets>septem</ets> seven: cf. F. <ets>sept⟦eacute⟧naire</ets>. See
<er>Seven</er>. ]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Consisting of, or relating to,
seven; <as>as, a <ex>septenary</ex> number</as>.</def> <rj><au>I.
Watts.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Lasting seven years; continuing seven years.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Septenary</xex> penance.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Fuller.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Septenary</ent>⟦br⟧

